quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,15,"Uye vakagadzika panyika makomo akamira zvakabata, kuti zvimwe ingabvunde nemi; uye nzizi nenzira, kuti muve munotungamirirwa"
  16,16,Uye zviratidzo (masikati) uye nenyenyedzi (husiku) munozvitungamirira
  16,17,Vakafanana here vanosika neuyo asingasiki? Hamurangariri here
  16,18,"Uye mukada kuverenga makomborero aAllah, hamukwanisi kumaverenga. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  16,19,Uye Allah vanoziva zvamunovanza nezvamunoburitsa
  16,20,"Avo (vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu) vavanokumbira kunze kwaAllah, havana kana chavakasika, asi ivo zvisikwa (vakasikwa)"
  16,21,"Zvitunha, havasi vapenyu, uye havazivi kuti vachamutswa rinhi"
  16,22,"Mwari wenyu ndiMwari vamwechete (Allah). Asi avo vasingatendi muhupenyu hwemangwana, moyo yavo inoramba (kutenda muhumwechete hwaAllah), uye vanozvikudza"
  16,23,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva zvavanovanza nezvavanoburitsa. Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) havadi vanozvikudza"
  16,24,"Uye kana zvikanzi kwavari: “Chii chakadzikiswa naTenzi venyu (kuna Muhammad (SAW))?” Vanoti: “Ingano dzemadzitateguru!”"
  16,25,"Vachatakura mutoro wavo zvizere pazuva rekumutswa, uye nemutoro weavo vavakarunzira (vavakarasisa) vasina ruzivo. Zvirokwazvo, uipi ndeizvo zvavachatakura"
  16,26,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vakanga varipo mushure mavo vakaronga, asi Allah vakaparadza migero yemidhadhadha (dzimba) yavo, uye denga (remba) rakadonha pasi pavari kubva pamusoro pavo, uye marwadzo akavabata kubva kune mativi avakanga vasina kutarisira"